<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, July 11 (Xinhua) -- Choy So-yuk was confirmed as a new
member of the Provisional Legislative Council (PLC) of the Hong
Kong Special Administrative Region (SAR) here today, at a meeting
of the chairman and vice-chairmen of the Preparatory Committee for
