house at the first floor of the 16-storey hotel, followed by heavy
explosions of gas containers. It soared to the top of the hotel
within one hour.
</P>
<P>
The fire was put under control about six hours later and about
80 percent of the hotel was damaged.
</P>
<P>
Officials said that the number of the people killed in the
disaster was likely to rise later.  
