<HEADLINE> Greece Plans to Set Up Agency to Boost Exports </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ATHENS, July 10 (Xinhua) -- Greece plans to set up an agency to
coordinate activities by the Greek enterprises in efforts to boost
the country's exports and investments in southeastern Europe.
